         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[H.K., Blackwarry, Gippsland ¶ Vic. ¶ — Baron von Mueller reports that the specimen of herb sent is from Lathyrus pativus, ¶ Typesetter's error for Lathyrus sativus? ¶  the Sacasse ¶ Typesetter’s erro...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">94.03.00b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Leader</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. The text given here is from 'Answers to correspondents. Specimen of plant', <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Leader</seg>, 31 March 1894, p. 5.</p>
               </note>
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[H.K., Blackwarry, Gippsland</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">— Baron von Mueller reports that the specimen of herb sent is from <name key="Lathyrus%20pativus">Lathyrus pativus</name>,</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Typesetter's error for <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Lathyrus</seg>
                        <seg style="font-style: italic; ">sativus</seg>?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> the Sacasse</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Typesetter’s error for 'Jarosse', the common name given by M in In B91.09.01, p. 252.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> of Southern Europe. A note on this species will be found in Mueller's</seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Select Plants</seg>
               <seg style="">, where he has drawn attention to the deleterious property of the seeds of this and some other kinds of Lathyrus. The hurtful principle is the cytisin, the same Alkaloids from which the poisonous quality of the Laburnum tree of our gardens are derived. This Alkaloid Is not developed in all species of Lathyrus, and vanishes in some of them by culture, but whether any such absolutely harmless varieties may relapse Into their normal natural state can only be found out through lengthened rural experiences.</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The details of the alkaloid are not given in the entry in B91.09.01. </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">]</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <name key="Lathyrus%20pativus">Lathyrus pativus</name>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
